Description: The irods package provides a set of R functions modeled after iRODS the icommands tools
             to allow file (data object) manipulation, storage and retrieval as well as searching.
License: BSD_3_clause
Imports: 
    Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: knitr,rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: To use rirods, a minimal installation of iRODS is required (
  irods-dev and irods-runtime). In addition clang6.0.0 is needed for compilation
  . Kerberos (libkrb5-dev) is needed for the authenticating of users and 
  services on a network. And the Jansson C library (jansson2.7-0) for encoding, 
  decoding and manipulating of JSON data.
